{"tid":1098941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣持枴杖老婦失控 擸菜刀狂劈滙豐櫃員機被捕","createTime":"2019-04-09T12:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T12:21:20.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e155b271304732ba4f63e887efe2a8239aaa2071","tid":1098941,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJ9scA6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJ9scA6.png&h=281c2c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長青邨一部櫃員機遭刑毀，警方拘捕一名涉案的老婦，並撿獲一把菜刀。黎家駒攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJMBQnW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJMBQnW.png&h=05a053e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KwArs9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwArs9C.png&h=d45397b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fv6qJHY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffv6qJHY.png&h=242e1b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員封鎖現場調查。黎家駒攝<br />\n<br />\n【18:45】更新圖片<br />\n<br />\n青衣發生刑毀案，下午4時許，長青邨有街坊報案，指一名手執枴杖的75歲老婦持菜刀狂劈商場平台一部滙豐櫃員機。警員接報到場，發現櫃員機螢幕玻璃爆裂，碎片散滿地上。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查，拘捕該名老婦，涉嫌刑毀，她報稱手指受傷，由救護車送院治理。警方在現場撿獲一架超市手推車、一把30厘米長菜刀及一枝柺杖，相信是被捕老婦遺下的。警方正調查老婦破壞櫃員機的原因，案件交由葵青警區刑事調查隊第5隊跟進。"},{"pid":"a21c90751bb26a77eaf9f0e7be586c277e0db13d","tid":1098941,"uid":218215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"癲婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c6082a35886281e3b31162fe4f6f8a334f25aa","tid":1098941,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"點解唔學天殘腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dce5e47c917f20551d01d60c474ede5e99d5ab","tid":1098941,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"阿婆好好力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}